# ============================================================
# ENGINEERING AI ASSISTANT - Environment Configuration
# ============================================================
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Fill in your OpenAI API key below
# 3. Run: pnpm install && pnpm dev
#
# For custom backend configuration, edit: /lib/api-config.ts
#
# ============================================================

# OpenAI API Key (Required for real AI responses)
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# ============================================================
# ALTERNATIVE: Use Mock Mode (No API key needed)
# ============================================================
# If you don't have an API key, you can enable mock mode:
# 1. Open /lib/api-config.ts
# 2. Set MOCK_MODE = true
# This will return simulated responses for testing.
